# Wealth Avatar — environment template. Copy to .env.local (gitignored).
#
# The demo runs fully offline on deterministic rules + templated avatar phrasing,
# so NO key is required to run or judge the prototype. The variable below is the
# seam for swapping the avatar's natural-language layer to Claude in production.
#
# Server-side only — never expose to the client, never commit the real value.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
